  "Description": {
    "English": "Spaceflight propulsion, boosts and on-demand Pulse Jumps through local system.<br> <br>User is advised that <span class=\"name name-exotic\">Tritium</span> is required to charge Pulse Engine. Tritium is abundant in <span class=\"name name-commodity\">near-space asteroid fields</span>. Locate Tritium with the starship scanner (<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>).<br><br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span> to engage Pulse Jump.<br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> to initiate in-flight speed boost.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "飞行推进装置，可加速并按照指令在本地恒星系中进行脉冲跃迁。<br><br>使用者请注意，必须用<span class=\"name name-exotic\">氚</span>给脉冲驱动器充能。<span class=\"name name-commodity\">近太空小行星带</span>含有丰富的氚。使用飞船扫描仪（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）以确定氚的位置。<br><br>同时按住<span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span>启动脉冲跃迁。<br>在飞行中按<span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span>启动加速。",
    "TencentChinese": "飞行推进装置，可加速并按照指令在本地恒星系中进行脉冲跳跃。<br> <br>使用者请注意，必须用<span class=\"name name-exotic\">氚</span>给脉冲驱动器充能。<span class=\"name name-commodity\">近太空小行星带</span>含有丰富的氚。<br><br>同时按住<span class=\"name name-img\">ROLLLEFT</span>和<span class=\"name name-img\">ROLLRIGHT</span>启动脉冲跳跃。<br>在飞行中按<span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span>启动加速。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "太空飛行推進器，能在當地星系加速並發動脈衝跳躍。<br> <br>提醒使用者，脈衝引擎需使用<span class=\"name name-exotic\">氚</span>充能。<span class=\"name name-commodity\">近太空的小行星帶</span>可以找到大量氚。使用太空船掃描器 (<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>) 找出氚。<br><br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">PULSEJUMP</span> 發動脈衝跳躍。<br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> 啟動飛行加速功能。"
  },
